    "Transparency and TrustworthinessThe size and complexity of deep learning models, particularly language models, have increased to the point where even the creators have difficulty comprehending why their models make specific predictions.",
    "This lack of interpretability is a major concern, particularly in situations where individuals want to understand the reasoning behind a model's output.",
    "The absence of transparency regarding the data sources used for generating output makes it challenging to properly cite the answers provided by ChatGPT.",
    "Further, LLMs lack the ability to provide uncertainty estimates [51].",
    "This makes it difficult for users to verify or have confidence in its output."
